# Day 2 Progress — SOC Infrastructure & Security Pipeline

## Overview

During Day 2, we successfully expanded the SOC architecture by integrating multiple cybersecurity layers including SIEM, IDS, WAF, attack simulation, centralized logging, and active response mechanisms.

