# Components Configured

## 1. Wazuh SIEM Setup

* Deployed Wazuh using Docker containers.
* Configured:

  * Wazuh Manager
  * Wazuh Dashboard
  * Wazuh Indexer
* Verified container health and service availability.
* Connected Kali Linux as a monitored Wazuh agent.
* Validated agent communication and event flow.

### Features Achieved

* Centralized log monitoring
* Security event visualization
* MITRE ATT&CK mapping
* Alert dashboards
* Agent monitoring

