# 3. IDS Integration — Suricata

Configured Suricata IDS to monitor network traffic and generate alerts.

### Alerts Observed

* Kali Linux DHCP detection
* Spotify P2P detection
* Network anomaly monitoring

### Integration

* Suricata logs forwarded into Wazuh
* Events visible inside Wazuh dashboard

