# 5. WAF Deployment — ModSecurity + OWASP CRS

Deployed ModSecurity Web Application Firewall using Docker.

### Technologies

* Nginx
* ModSecurity
* OWASP Core Rule Set (CRS)

### WAF Capabilities

* SQL Injection detection
* Request blocking
* HTTP 403 response generation
* CRS rule enforcement

---

# 6. SQL Injection Detection Testing

Executed SQL injection payloads against the WAF.

### Payload Used

?id=' OR 1=1 --

### Results

* Request blocked successfully
* 403 Forbidden returned
* ModSecurity alerts generated

### Triggered CRS Rules

* REQUEST-949-BLOCKING-EVALUATION.conf
* Inbound Anomaly Score Exceeded

